[[iftags 组件]]
使用方法请参见[[[the-alleys-other-goif|指南]]].
[[/iftags]]

[[iftags -组件]]
[[module CSS]]
.scp-woi-block {
    border-left: #000 1px solid;
    border-right: #000 1px solid;
    border-top: #000 1px solid;
    border-bottom: none;
    background-color: #fcfcfc;
    color: #000000;
}

.scp-woi-title {
    color: #292929;
    font-weight: bolder;
    border-bottom: #000 1px solid;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #C2EBF2, #7AC0CC);
    padding-top: 0.3em;
    padding-right: 1em;
    padding-left: 1em;
    padding-bottom: 1em;
}

.scp-woi-caption {
    background-color: none;
    padding-top: 0.5em;
    padding-right: 2em;
    padding-left: 2em;
    padding-bottom: 1em;
}

.scp-woi-image {
    background-color: #fff;
    border: #000 1px solid;
}

.scp-woi-forum-0 { 
    background-color: none;
    border-top: #000 1px solid;
    padding-top: 1em;
    padding-right: 1em;
    padding-left: 1em;
    padding-bottom: 0.5em;
}
[[/module]]

[[/div]]

